You are given the following reduction reactions and $E^{\circ}$ values:
$$
\begin{array}{ll}
\mathrm{Fe}^{3+}(a q)+\mathrm{e}^{-} \rightarrow \mathrm{Fe}^{2+}(a q) & E^{\circ}=+0.771 \mathrm{~V} \\
